data.description: Welcome to this gorgeous neighborhood! CUL-DE-SAC.  Terrific Split Level home with its spacious and open floor plan that's just perfect for all your needs. With 4 bedrooms and 3 bathrooms, there's room for everyone to have their own space. This home has just been updated in 2020 with a completely transformed kitchen that includes new stainless steel appliances, Quartz countertops and freshly painted cabinets. The home also feature all-new exterior paint, new light fixtures. 1/2 Acre to enjoy the back patio, perfect for barbecues. HVAC unit (2018). Roof less than 10 years. Don't wait! Make this beautiful home yours today. NO HOA! AS IS CONDITION.
